<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1179879-as-i-begin-this-574-page-journey-i-would">As I begin this 574 page journey, I would like to know what others who are further along think of this book? I have become weary of the civil war culture, the war was fought over slavery and the generals who are honored from both sides sent men into battles that resulted in horrific casualties so I don&#39;t see a reason for honoring such acts, hell even I could lose 20,000 men in a battle!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1179879'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18144074-rebel-yell">like</a></span>

