<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1384350-an-interminably-dull-book-about-a">An interminably dull book about a Confederate psychopath who delighted in killing, with all the fanaticism of a religious zealot. Told with barely supressed pro-Southern sentiments, clearly taking cues from Shelby Foote. 

Need help falling asleep? This will surely help.</a>
</div>
