<div id="review_2016873113" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2016873113" />
    <a title="Anthony Whitt" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/22020599-anthony-whitt"><img alt="Anthony Whitt" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442949965p2/22020599.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2016873113?book_show_action=true">Jun 26, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anthony Whitt" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anthony Whitt" href="/user/show/22020599-anthony-whitt">Anthony Whitt</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2016873113" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16482018745549919003">One of the best biographies you will ever read. Gwynne introduces you to Stonewall Jackson and you will come to understand he is every bit the legendary Civil War leader you have heard about. But Gwynne also takes you on an exploration of the man behind the hard driving commander that excelled on the battlefield. Be prepared to form an emotional attachment with Jackson well crafted by an outstanding author. Excellent work and highly recommended! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


